## AI Service Accomplishments

Added two new REST endpoints to `ai_service/main.py`:
- `POST /parse-gstr2b`: Accepts government GSTR-2B JSON file outputs, flatter-mapping them into structured invoice lines.
- `POST /parse-26as`: Accepts Form 26AS PDF/Text files copy-pasted directly from the income tax portal, parsing withholding tax lines, section codes, and rates via regex matching.

