## Frontend Accomplishments

Created 5 beautiful new dashboard/compliance views inside `frontend/src/pages/`:
1. **`GSTRecon.tsx`**: Period selector, drag & drop GSTR-2B JSON file upload, Purchase Register CSV file upload, and matching engine runs with visible warnings on tax variances.
2. **`TDSRecon.tsx`**: Financial year and quarter selectors, Form 26AS document parsing, internal TDS ledger matching, and mismatch summary alerts.
3. **`VendorRisk.tsx`**: Interactive risk badges, rolling risk profile stats (average resolution days, amount-at-risk), and block/unblock release action buttons. Clicking on a row pulls up a detailed side profile drawer showing their exceptions history timeline.
4. **`MonthEndClose.tsx`**: Compliance progress status tracker, checklist generated task items list, completion checkboxes, deep links to specific views, and formal period close buttons.
5. **`Integrations.tsx`**: Forms to connect local TallyPrime hosts and Zoho Books cloud organizations (supporting OAuth save & test connection validations), and an interactive Sync Jobs logs history table.

- Registered navigation elements in `Sidebar.tsx` and child path mappings in `main.tsx`.
- Defined TypeScript type interfaces in `types/index.ts` and added the `patch` request method in `api/client.ts`.
- Ran `tsc --noEmit` locally, which built successfully with zero TypeScript compiler errors!
